# Marker file for magic mount / Hybrid Mount.
#
# This directory (/system/priv-app/CarrierImsApplier/) does NOT exist on the
# stock system. Without this marker, magic mount (bind mount) skips it because
# there is no existing target to bind over. The `.replace` marker tells the
# mount backend to treat the entire containing directory as a replacement —
# creating it even when it is absent from the stock partition.
